headline: T-Mobile (TMUS) Completes UScellular Merger, Eyes $1.2 Billion Annual Cost Savings
summary: T-Mobile US, Inc. (NASDAQ:TMUS) ranks among the best communication services stocks to buy now. On September 4, T-Mobile US, Inc. (NASDAQ:TMUS) stated that it anticipates increasing its service revenue by around $400 million this quarter as it merges users of recently acquired regional rival UScellular.
